{"tid":1854891,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"簡單話你知點解要撐醫護罷工","createTime":"2020-01-31T17:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T16:57:51.000Z","uid":68531,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"58efab3607ddeaa9bcfac0e9cdb9b6bc959ceae1","tid":1854891,"uid":68531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T17:47:39.000Z","msg":"For TLDR:<br />\n<br />\n醫護罷工&mdash;&gt;政府跪低<br />\n<br />\n=1:0 先贏一仗<br />\n<br />\n外加比全香港人知罷工係work <br />\n工會將加速發展 全港真。大三罷指日可待<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫護罷工&mdash;&gt;政府企硬<br />\n<br />\n=0.5:0 先贏半球<br />\n<br />\n因為醫療系統停滯 後果大家可想而知<br />\n到時大家可以將呢球12碼交比林鄭守龍<br />\n分分鐘connect埋藍絲 屌9柒婆把守不力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n講到尾 醫護罷工勢在必行<br />\n我地除左打卡講支持之外<br />\n我希望大家都有加入罷工一員嘅心理準備<br />\n工會列表：<a href=\"https://hkonstrike.com/unions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkonstrike.com%2Funions&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=9a0a47ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkonstrike.com/unions</a><br />\n<br />\n另外中期後就講 大家準備好係疫情退散（可遲可早）後要即刻舉行大遊行，旨在指責政府防疫零效率<br />\n好多人已經淡忘左要對準政權 但始終差佬實在冇令大家失望 不斷比驚喜大家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權，最佳方法係連呢班守護住政權嘅condom都connect到。<br />\n係呀，唔易架，要香港人接受都難。但係，想贏，就係要做啲大家都難接受嘅事。要記住，多一個隊友比起樹敵更重要。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我支持醫護罷工</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我準備好大三罷</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我要對準政權</span></span>"},{"pid":"07b2b6de5152bd0d51d010e31531dff755652906","tid":1854891,"uid":68531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T17:47:58.000Z","msg":"我要入工會"},{"pid":"d81e8046be91abc2a016ab0501fcdf4f0f1481ca","tid":1854891,"uid":68531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco